1
00:00:21,830 --> 00:00:23,190
What do you make of

2
00:00:24,190 --> 00:00:25,390
what happened today?

3
00:00:25,760 --> 00:00:27,640
Xiao Wuyi and Xie Jiayu

4
00:00:27,800 --> 00:00:29,830
were targeting Li Lejun from the start.

5
00:00:29,830 --> 00:00:33,110
Li Lejun really did plot
against the Princess.

6
00:00:34,110 --> 00:00:37,150
But Xiao Wuyi and Xie Jiayu
may have framed her

7
00:00:37,880 --> 00:00:38,670
as well.

8
00:00:39,310 --> 00:00:40,600
Your Majesty means

9
00:00:40,880 --> 00:00:42,910
there is a third Phoenix Heart Token—

10
00:00:42,910 --> 00:00:45,110
the one Empress Wenxi once gave Xiao Ju.

11
00:00:45,560 --> 00:00:47,240
Then, where is the Princess's

12
00:00:47,390 --> 00:00:48,790
Phoenix Heart Token now?

13
00:00:50,560 --> 00:00:51,390
Li Mao.

14
00:00:52,560 --> 00:00:53,820
I underestimated him.

15
00:00:54,750 --> 00:00:57,680
Just now, when Li Lejun
was arrested and imprisoned,

16
00:00:57,920 --> 00:00:59,920
he didn't say a word in her defense.

17
00:01:00,960 --> 00:01:01,770
Li Mao.

18
00:01:03,070 --> 00:01:04,480
Xie Jiayu.

19
00:01:05,349 --> 00:01:06,680
Xiao Wuyi.

20
00:01:08,230 --> 00:01:09,230
See?

21
00:01:10,760 --> 00:01:12,620
Things are getting interesting.

22
00:02:41,090 --> 00:02:45,250
[Key to the Phoenix Heart]

23
00:02:45,460 --> 00:02:48,180
[Episode 19]

24
00:03:08,520 --> 00:03:11,380
You came from the lowest ranks
of society yourself.

25
00:03:13,190 --> 00:03:15,150
Since you decided to take this position,

26
00:03:15,150 --> 00:03:16,710
you should have a more compassionate heart

27
00:03:16,710 --> 00:03:18,440
and a greater sense of purpose.

28
00:03:28,960 --> 00:03:30,079
Little beggar.

29
00:03:32,400 --> 00:03:33,360
Come on.

30
00:03:39,470 --> 00:03:40,400
Eat slowly.

31
00:03:42,590 --> 00:03:43,790
Where is your family?

32
00:03:44,910 --> 00:03:45,710
They're dead.

33
00:03:48,150 --> 00:03:49,210
Where are you from?

34
00:03:49,360 --> 00:03:50,120
Qizhou.

35
00:03:50,630 --> 00:03:51,760
Where are you going?

36
00:03:51,840 --> 00:03:52,520
Jiankang.

37
00:04:00,640 --> 00:04:01,450
Who is it?

38
00:04:03,430 --> 00:04:06,310
I am here to bring Your Highness
a calming herbal tonic.

39
00:04:06,310 --> 00:04:07,240
You again.

40
00:04:08,430 --> 00:04:09,760
Still haven't given up?

41
00:04:24,920 --> 00:04:25,950
Then stay.

42
00:04:28,160 --> 00:04:29,620
Thank you, Your Highness.

43
00:04:40,750 --> 00:04:41,680
Smile more.

44
00:04:43,680 --> 00:04:45,740
You look like her only when you smile.

45
00:05:00,040 --> 00:05:00,840
What's wrong?

46
00:05:01,400 --> 00:05:04,380
[Xuanzheng Hall]

47
00:05:07,720 --> 00:05:10,450
Mother never brought me
to the palace in the past.

48
00:05:11,270 --> 00:05:12,950
She said there is nothing fun.

49
00:05:15,600 --> 00:05:17,130
Today is my first time here,

50
00:05:17,390 --> 00:05:19,590
and it's true that there's nothing fun.

51
00:05:19,920 --> 00:05:21,650
I never want to come here again.

52
00:05:24,720 --> 00:05:25,390
Okay.

53
00:05:27,560 --> 00:05:28,430
Then don't.

54
00:05:34,159 --> 00:05:35,950
You just gave Cui Jun's
Phoenix Heart Token

55
00:05:35,950 --> 00:05:37,000
away like that?

56
00:05:37,870 --> 00:05:38,600
Don't worry.

57
00:05:39,310 --> 00:05:40,750
Since I dared to give it away,

58
00:05:40,750 --> 00:05:41,680
I can get it back.

59
00:05:42,310 --> 00:05:44,370
I'll get the Cui family's mine first.

60
00:05:45,640 --> 00:05:46,440
Let's go home.

61
00:06:11,830 --> 00:06:13,310
Not burying Her Highness

62
00:06:14,120 --> 00:06:15,720
until Li Lejun was captured—

63
00:06:16,160 --> 00:06:17,560
was that a promise to her?

64
00:06:18,430 --> 00:06:19,630
Do souls really exist

65
00:06:20,920 --> 00:06:22,360
after death?

66
00:06:27,950 --> 00:06:28,870
She will know.

67
00:06:32,040 --> 00:06:33,300
As long as you believe,

68
00:06:34,070 --> 00:06:34,950
she exists

69
00:06:35,750 --> 00:06:36,560
and will know.

70
00:06:38,480 --> 00:06:39,390
Is this how you

71
00:06:40,070 --> 00:06:41,610
commemorate your parents?

72
00:06:46,310 --> 00:06:47,840
Maybe I shouldn't say that.

73
00:06:50,310 --> 00:06:51,440
I've never met them,

74
00:06:51,940 --> 00:06:53,200
but I get curious, too.

75
00:06:53,950 --> 00:06:55,950
Just like when you listen to a story,

76
00:06:56,000 --> 00:06:57,950
you'd wonder how the person in the story

77
00:06:57,950 --> 00:06:59,159
is related to you.

78
00:07:00,040 --> 00:07:01,270
But in this world,

79
00:07:02,070 --> 00:07:05,200
you can't empathize
without experiencing it yourself.

80
00:07:05,560 --> 00:07:07,490
So I can't say it's commemoration.

81
00:07:07,600 --> 00:07:09,600
The Xiao family gave me everything.

82
00:07:09,870 --> 00:07:11,070
The power in my hands,

83
00:07:12,190 --> 00:07:13,450
the ambition I uphold,

84
00:07:14,160 --> 00:07:15,360
the bonds I hold dear,

85
00:07:16,040 --> 00:07:17,360
and the mission I bear.

86
00:07:18,040 --> 00:07:19,600
Whether glory or disgrace,

87
00:07:20,630 --> 00:07:23,690
none of this has anything
to do with Crown Prince Wenxi.

88
00:07:23,720 --> 00:07:24,950
I am looking for the Phoenix Heart Token

89
00:07:24,950 --> 00:07:26,240
for the minerals behind it,

90
00:07:26,240 --> 00:07:28,000
which can be used to make caltrop fireball

91
00:07:28,000 --> 00:07:28,870
to serve Ye.

92
00:07:30,270 --> 00:07:31,240
The path I chose

93
00:07:31,800 --> 00:07:33,390
was never in the court.

94
00:07:35,040 --> 00:07:36,500
I just want to be Xiao Wuyi.

95
00:07:37,630 --> 00:07:38,310
That night,

96
00:07:38,560 --> 00:07:40,240
you saw me arguing with Her Highness.

97
00:07:40,240 --> 00:07:42,240
That was what we were talking about.

98
00:07:42,390 --> 00:07:44,190
I never wanted to implicate her.

99
00:07:44,950 --> 00:07:46,280
Who says we stand alone?

100
00:07:47,000 --> 00:07:48,240
We share weal and woe.

101
00:07:50,310 --> 00:07:51,190
I see.

102
00:07:52,240 --> 00:07:53,440
No wonder Mother said

103
00:07:54,159 --> 00:07:55,430
you have a good name.

104
00:07:58,180 --> 00:08:00,040
But now the Cui family has fallen,

105
00:08:00,310 --> 00:08:01,830
and Mother has passed away.

106
00:08:01,830 --> 00:08:03,430
Only the Xiao family is left.

107
00:08:03,630 --> 00:08:05,160
You control the Beifu army.

108
00:08:05,240 --> 00:08:07,830
Prince Jing'an's Household will become
even more threatening in their eyes.

109
00:08:07,830 --> 00:08:08,830
Your identity

110
00:08:09,680 --> 00:08:11,740
might not be hidden anymore, either.

111
00:08:14,240 --> 00:08:15,170
It should be them

112
00:08:15,920 --> 00:08:16,830
who are afraid

113
00:08:16,830 --> 00:08:19,360
that I will admit
to being Crown Prince Wenxi.

114
00:08:25,440 --> 00:08:27,130
[Prince Jing'an's Mansion]

115
00:08:28,680 --> 00:08:29,750
Your Highness!

116
00:08:29,750 --> 00:08:30,920
Auntie Xie!

117
00:08:30,920 --> 00:08:32,030
You're back.

118
00:08:32,360 --> 00:08:35,419
I made Auntie's favorite
wild-green flatbread today.

119
00:08:53,080 --> 00:08:54,680
I'll accept your black iron.

120
00:08:55,600 --> 00:08:56,480
But actually,

121
00:08:59,440 --> 00:09:01,170
there is something I want more.

122
00:09:01,270 --> 00:09:02,240
What do you want?

123
00:09:04,150 --> 00:09:05,030
Your courage.

124
00:09:05,720 --> 00:09:06,510
Courage?

125
00:09:09,960 --> 00:09:12,560
Being kind and soft-hearted
is not your fault.

126
00:09:13,910 --> 00:09:15,360
Don't let past betrayals

127
00:09:16,440 --> 00:09:19,440
make you completely lose
the courage to trust others.

128
00:09:22,480 --> 00:09:24,010
You still have new friends,

129
00:09:26,510 --> 00:09:28,040
and you will have a new home.

130
00:09:33,750 --> 00:09:36,080
Actually, before I went to Lingfeng Fort,

131
00:09:37,200 --> 00:09:39,130
I had never really seen suffering.

132
00:09:40,590 --> 00:09:41,990
I grew up in the Xie family

133
00:09:42,000 --> 00:09:43,400
and was raised by Mother.

134
00:09:44,030 --> 00:09:45,430
I thought I was oppressed

135
00:09:45,650 --> 00:09:48,180
simply because I had no say
in my own marriage.

136
00:09:48,200 --> 00:09:49,530
Only later did I realize

137
00:09:49,960 --> 00:09:50,690
that there is

138
00:09:51,790 --> 00:09:53,720
no true haven of peace

139
00:09:54,750 --> 00:09:56,410
and simplicity in this world.

140
00:09:59,390 --> 00:10:00,630
Master once asked me,

141
00:10:01,790 --> 00:10:03,150
"Where is the martial arts world?

142
00:10:03,150 --> 00:10:05,150
And where are the ends of the earth?"

143
00:10:05,790 --> 00:10:06,600
Now,

144
00:10:08,750 --> 00:10:09,720
I understand.

145
00:10:10,800 --> 00:10:13,260
It's always been like this
in chaotic times.

146
00:10:14,080 --> 00:10:16,940
Beneath the feasts and revelry
lie blood and tears.

147
00:10:19,150 --> 00:10:21,280
It is already difficult to stay alive.

148
00:10:23,320 --> 00:10:23,960
Okay.

149
00:10:24,510 --> 00:10:25,390
I promise you.

150
00:10:28,870 --> 00:10:30,670
I'll still have faith in others.

151
00:10:35,720 --> 00:10:36,720
I also promise you

152
00:10:37,960 --> 00:10:40,090
that I will help you uncover the secret
of the Phoenix Heart Token,

153
00:10:40,090 --> 00:10:42,950
find the connection
between the token and the mine,

154
00:10:43,550 --> 00:10:45,880
and help you create the caltrop fireball.

155
00:10:48,550 --> 00:10:49,720
Do you know what

156
00:10:50,630 --> 00:10:51,760
your promise means?

157
00:10:52,720 --> 00:10:54,180
Kindness is not a mistake.

158
00:10:54,450 --> 00:10:59,610
♪ What's the cost
of going against the wind? ♪

159
00:10:55,790 --> 00:10:57,320
But kindness without power

160
00:10:58,030 --> 00:10:59,560
is no better than weakness.

161
00:11:00,440 --> 00:11:04,120
♪ Knowing you, knowing me,
we live up to our promises ♪

162
00:11:00,960 --> 00:11:02,620
This applies to individuals,

163
00:11:03,030 --> 00:11:05,150
and it applies to nations as well.

164
00:11:04,150 --> 00:11:08,350
♪ Aligning the traces of our conviction ♪

165
00:11:06,600 --> 00:11:07,720
Ye needs Beifu,

166
00:11:08,200 --> 00:11:09,550
otherwise peace is just empty talk.

167
00:11:08,460 --> 00:11:10,930
♪ As long as I'm with you ♪

168
00:11:10,550 --> 00:11:12,080
And Beifu needs the caltrop fireball

169
00:11:10,960 --> 00:11:13,940
♪ The journey can stretch on forever ♪

170
00:11:12,600 --> 00:11:14,720
to deter enemies or noble families,

171
00:11:13,960 --> 00:11:17,710
♪ Even if it puts my life on the line ♪

172
00:11:16,510 --> 00:11:17,360
even

173
00:11:17,740 --> 00:11:20,430
♪ I shall never forget ♪

174
00:11:18,360 --> 00:11:20,720
it may bring uncontrollable energy.

175
00:11:20,520 --> 00:11:24,900
♪ Let me dash toward where you are ♪

176
00:11:22,910 --> 00:11:24,440
Words alone are not enough.

177
00:11:24,670 --> 00:11:26,080
So let's deter them with power.

178
00:11:24,930 --> 00:11:28,360
♪ To seek out my own sanctuary ♪

179
00:11:27,870 --> 00:11:28,670
Xiao Wuyi.

180
00:11:28,380 --> 00:11:31,170
♪ Life hurries by, yet you alone ♪

181
00:11:30,720 --> 00:11:32,440
Let me be your strongest support.

182
00:11:31,190 --> 00:11:34,190
♪ Illuminate me
with your blazing radiance ♪

183
00:11:34,150 --> 00:11:35,200
You and me—

184
00:11:34,210 --> 00:11:38,270
♪ Let me burn with courage
as I forge ahead ♪

185
00:11:37,750 --> 00:11:38,510
Let's go together.

186
00:11:38,290 --> 00:11:41,780
♪ Your hand in my hand ♪

187
00:11:41,800 --> 00:11:44,720
♪ Our love knows no bounds
of time or space ♪

188
00:11:44,750 --> 00:11:50,270
♪ Two hearts together
until the end of time ♪

189
00:11:55,240 --> 00:11:59,290
♪ Let me burn with courage
as I forge ahead ♪

190
00:11:59,430 --> 00:12:02,920
♪ Your hand in my hand ♪

191
00:12:02,940 --> 00:12:05,860
♪ Our love knows no bounds
of time or space ♪

192
00:12:05,890 --> 00:12:11,420
♪ Two hearts together
until the end of time ♪

193
00:12:39,960 --> 00:12:40,760
What's wrong?

194
00:12:41,000 --> 00:12:42,720
You walking in here without saying a word

195
00:12:42,720 --> 00:12:44,000
is scarier than when you stumble in

196
00:12:44,000 --> 00:12:45,030
covered in blood.

197
00:12:46,550 --> 00:12:49,200
You said before
that the blood stasis in my brain

198
00:12:49,200 --> 00:12:50,660
would affect my lifespan.

199
00:12:52,240 --> 00:12:53,750
You'll go blind in two or three years,

200
00:12:53,750 --> 00:12:56,080
and you'll die within three to five years.

201
00:13:01,910 --> 00:13:03,480
Can you help me live longer?

202
00:13:07,360 --> 00:13:08,440
Didn't you say

203
00:13:08,870 --> 00:13:10,600
three to five years was enough?

204
00:13:11,360 --> 00:13:13,560
Why do you suddenly want to live longer?

205
00:13:13,810 --> 00:13:14,870
Can you or not?

206
00:13:23,390 --> 00:13:24,270
Yes,

207
00:13:25,030 --> 00:13:26,490
as long as you listen to me.

208
00:13:32,270 --> 00:13:33,550
If it's a key,

209
00:13:33,840 --> 00:13:35,390
what does it unlock?

210
00:13:35,820 --> 00:13:38,550
It would still require
all 4 pieces put together.

211
00:13:40,320 --> 00:13:42,000
Cui Jun only had one piece

212
00:13:42,480 --> 00:13:44,360
and found one of the mines.

213
00:13:46,440 --> 00:13:47,840
This means it's not a key,

214
00:13:48,160 --> 00:13:49,400
but the totem itself.

215
00:13:50,240 --> 00:13:53,000
The Phoenix Imperial Seal was reforged
into the form of the Vermilion Bird,

216
00:13:53,000 --> 00:13:54,630
with its head and tail
forming a complete whole.

217
00:13:54,630 --> 00:13:56,630
What secret lies within this totem?

218
00:13:58,480 --> 00:13:59,390
Yuanji?

219
00:14:03,000 --> 00:14:04,270
I'm really seeing things.

220
00:14:04,270 --> 00:14:05,600
How could it be Yuanji?

221
00:14:08,160 --> 00:14:08,710
My Lady,

222
00:14:09,320 --> 00:14:10,720
drink it while it's warm.

223
00:14:10,720 --> 00:14:12,080
It clears heat and improves vision.

224
00:14:12,080 --> 00:14:14,080
I just got these herbs from Qing Long.

225
00:14:14,080 --> 00:14:15,200
From Qing Long?

226
00:14:15,960 --> 00:14:17,030
What's wrong with his eyes?

227
00:14:17,030 --> 00:14:19,030
It's because of Cui Jun's kidnapping.

228
00:14:19,030 --> 00:14:20,870
Qing Long was in charge
of keeping the key.

229
00:14:20,870 --> 00:14:22,550
He said the key was never lost.

230
00:14:23,080 --> 00:14:24,240
Even when sleeping,

231
00:14:24,280 --> 00:14:25,510
he kept it close to him.

232
00:14:25,510 --> 00:14:26,480
But the lock

233
00:14:26,480 --> 00:14:28,080
had no signs of being pried.

234
00:14:28,790 --> 00:14:30,480
Qing Long said that unless he was blind,

235
00:14:30,480 --> 00:14:33,140
it couldn't have happened
without him knowing.

236
00:14:33,670 --> 00:14:34,550
Yuanji.

237
00:14:35,290 --> 00:14:37,320
What's wrong with the Heir's Consort?

238
00:14:37,320 --> 00:14:39,150
She is the Empress Dowager's niece.

239
00:14:39,150 --> 00:14:41,740
Why are you saying
such strange things, My Lady?

240
00:14:41,740 --> 00:14:42,740
Of course, she

241
00:14:42,760 --> 00:14:44,560
is the Empress Dowager's niece.

242
00:14:46,550 --> 00:14:47,150
No.

243
00:14:47,270 --> 00:14:48,870
That's not right, Xie Jiayu.

244
00:14:48,870 --> 00:14:50,270
How could you think that?

245
00:14:51,120 --> 00:14:52,580
Yuanji treats you so well.

246
00:14:53,390 --> 00:14:54,360
How could she?

247
00:15:06,200 --> 00:15:08,400
I told you I'm already thinking of a way.

248
00:15:08,840 --> 00:15:11,000
Her Majesty misses her sister.

249
00:15:11,440 --> 00:15:13,420
[He Yuanji's Father]
[He Yuanji's Mother]

250
00:15:11,510 --> 00:15:13,510
She invites your mother
to the palace for a chat.

251
00:15:13,510 --> 00:15:15,040
She'll be back in a few days.

252
00:15:15,470 --> 00:15:18,160
I just came to inform Your Highness.

253
00:15:19,600 --> 00:15:21,080
The Empress Dowager has gone too far.

254
00:15:21,080 --> 00:15:21,960
Over the years,

255
00:15:21,960 --> 00:15:24,030
Her Majesty let you stay
at Prince Jing'an's Mansion

256
00:15:24,030 --> 00:15:25,270
without doing anything,

257
00:15:25,270 --> 00:15:27,360
only to deliver a fatal blow today.

258
00:15:27,790 --> 00:15:28,790
No matter what,

259
00:15:28,790 --> 00:15:30,590
you are a member of the He family.

260
00:15:30,960 --> 00:15:33,200
The lives of hundreds
of people in your family

261
00:15:33,200 --> 00:15:34,840
are in Her Majesty's hands.

262
00:15:35,360 --> 00:15:37,030
You'd better weigh your options carefully.

263
00:15:37,030 --> 00:15:38,910
I already helped
Her Majesty kidnap Cui Jun.

264
00:15:38,910 --> 00:15:40,480
How can I get the Phoenix Heart Token now?

265
00:15:40,480 --> 00:15:42,010
You figure it out yourself.

266
00:15:42,200 --> 00:15:43,550
I heard Your Highness

267
00:15:43,550 --> 00:15:45,970
has been visiting
Zhengtong Bookstore frequently lately.

268
00:15:45,970 --> 00:15:47,790
Is there someone there who reminds you
of an old acquaintance,

269
00:15:47,790 --> 00:15:50,030
someone you still hold dear?

270
00:15:50,240 --> 00:15:52,360
If you refuse to find a way,

271
00:15:52,600 --> 00:15:55,480
Her Majesty will find one herself.

272
00:16:00,790 --> 00:16:01,840
The place where Cui Jun was held

273
00:16:01,840 --> 00:16:03,650
was His Highness's
hidden house in Jiankang.

274
00:16:03,650 --> 00:16:04,390
No one could escape from there,

275
00:16:04,390 --> 00:16:05,550
and no one even knows it exists.

276
00:16:05,550 --> 00:16:06,510
Cui Jun lost a hand,

277
00:16:06,510 --> 00:16:07,840
yet he vanished into thin air.

278
00:16:07,840 --> 00:16:08,910
It's like something out of a ghost story.

279
00:16:08,910 --> 00:16:09,600
There is only one key

280
00:16:09,600 --> 00:16:10,670
to the hidden house in the world,

281
00:16:10,670 --> 00:16:12,480
and His Highness entrusted it to me.

282
00:16:12,480 --> 00:16:13,540
I swear upon Heaven

283
00:16:13,630 --> 00:16:14,670
that I never leaked the key,

284
00:16:14,670 --> 00:16:16,270
nor did I help Cui Jun escape.

285
00:16:18,200 --> 00:16:19,120
On the day of the palace banquet,

286
00:16:19,120 --> 00:16:21,550
His Highness traded the Phoenix Heart Token
for the Cui family's mines.

287
00:16:21,550 --> 00:16:22,960
The noble families didn't get a share.

288
00:16:22,960 --> 00:16:24,150
They thought they had suffered a loss,

289
00:16:24,150 --> 00:16:25,870
so they joined forces
to accuse His Highness,

290
00:16:25,870 --> 00:16:28,230
saying his reform
of Beifu was for himself.

291
00:16:28,230 --> 00:16:29,320
These old geezers

292
00:16:29,790 --> 00:16:31,200
are clearly making a fuss over nothing

293
00:16:31,200 --> 00:16:32,460
to frame His Highness.

294
00:16:32,960 --> 00:16:34,000
He really didn't do it himself?

295
00:16:34,000 --> 00:16:35,000
Oh, Lady Xie.

296
00:16:35,000 --> 00:16:35,790
Alright.

297
00:16:35,960 --> 00:16:36,750
Calm down.

298
00:16:37,440 --> 00:16:38,770
I believe it wasn't him.

299
00:16:39,440 --> 00:16:41,630
But it's indeed quite suspicious.

300
00:16:42,080 --> 00:16:43,200
Hiding the person on purpose

301
00:16:43,200 --> 00:16:44,600
to see how everyone reacts.

302
00:16:44,600 --> 00:16:47,510
Would you call this a feint
or taking advantage of the chaos

303
00:16:47,510 --> 00:16:48,750
in military strategy?

304
00:16:48,750 --> 00:16:50,000
Not this time.

305
00:16:51,030 --> 00:16:51,840
Then Xiao Wuyi

306
00:16:52,000 --> 00:16:53,600
just going to let them frame him?

307
00:16:53,600 --> 00:16:55,270
Hasn't His Highness always been like this?

308
00:16:55,270 --> 00:16:57,510
He never cares what others say or think.

309
00:17:04,920 --> 00:17:05,480
My Lady,

310
00:17:06,109 --> 00:17:08,770
the Heir's Consort
is indeed not in the mansion.

311
00:17:11,160 --> 00:17:13,290
Outsiders had no chance to get near it,

312
00:17:13,589 --> 00:17:15,450
but what if it was someone inside?

313
00:17:21,310 --> 00:17:21,829
Anmin.

314
00:17:23,880 --> 00:17:25,680
You went to the bookstore again?

315
00:17:26,200 --> 00:17:27,589
I found another

316
00:17:27,589 --> 00:17:29,260
extremely precious ancient book today.

317
00:17:29,260 --> 00:17:29,820
Right,

318
00:17:30,000 --> 00:17:32,200
I also found some ancient books
on canal building.

319
00:17:32,200 --> 00:17:34,070
They were left by craftsmen
who followed Li Luhai

320
00:17:34,070 --> 00:17:35,920
when they built the Qin Canal in the past.

321
00:17:35,920 --> 00:17:37,350
You currently hold

322
00:17:37,350 --> 00:17:39,400
the position overseeing the construction
of the new canal.

323
00:17:39,400 --> 00:17:41,070
These books

324
00:17:41,070 --> 00:17:42,070
might also be very important to you.

325
00:17:42,070 --> 00:17:44,130
I'll have them copied and sent to you.

326
00:17:44,240 --> 00:17:46,300
I didn't expect you to keep it in mind.

327
00:17:46,750 --> 00:17:48,790
But it's chaotic outside these few days.

328
00:17:48,790 --> 00:17:50,050
You should go out less.

329
00:17:53,440 --> 00:17:53,960
Got it.

330
00:17:55,750 --> 00:17:56,350
Yuanji.

331
00:17:58,200 --> 00:17:59,530
Is there anything else?

332
00:18:02,160 --> 00:18:04,490
Bring more people
with you when you go out.

333
00:18:04,510 --> 00:18:05,030
Okay.

334
00:18:25,310 --> 00:18:26,840
I'm not playing Go with you.

335
00:18:27,270 --> 00:18:28,830
You're even worse at Go than Father.

336
00:18:28,830 --> 00:18:29,760
I'm in a bad mood.

337
00:18:29,880 --> 00:18:30,940
Play a game with me.

338
00:18:32,110 --> 00:18:33,510
Rather than spending your time here,

339
00:18:33,510 --> 00:18:35,480
why don't you just be honest with her?

340
00:18:35,480 --> 00:18:36,640
It's been five years.

341
00:18:36,640 --> 00:18:37,920
Anmin, you really know
how to drag things out.

342
00:18:37,920 --> 00:18:38,400
You—

343
00:18:39,270 --> 00:18:39,920
Xiao Wuyi.

344
00:18:40,610 --> 00:18:41,830
She is your Consort.

345
00:18:42,790 --> 00:18:45,320
You never care
about having a bad reputation,

346
00:18:45,660 --> 00:18:47,010
but she's a woman.

347
00:18:47,830 --> 00:18:48,830
Can she not care?

348
00:18:49,510 --> 00:18:50,400
If I tell her,

349
00:18:51,240 --> 00:18:53,440
how can she gain a foothold
in Jiankang?

350
00:18:53,720 --> 00:18:55,410
She is not as pedantic as you.

351
00:18:55,740 --> 00:18:56,260
You.

352
00:19:00,440 --> 00:19:01,170
What is this?

353
00:19:06,750 --> 00:19:09,080
I've already given her the divorce paper.

354
00:19:09,080 --> 00:19:10,240
She is free now.

355
00:19:11,480 --> 00:19:13,000
Don't blame me for not reminding you.

356
00:19:13,000 --> 00:19:14,120
If you don't make a move soon,

357
00:19:14,120 --> 00:19:15,180
they might rekindle their old flame,

358
00:19:15,180 --> 00:19:16,990
and you'll regret it when it's too late.

359
00:19:16,990 --> 00:19:18,430
Liu Zhaolin is really...

360
00:19:37,160 --> 00:19:38,910
The Heir's Consort has gone out again?

361
00:19:38,910 --> 00:19:40,200
Yes, she just left.

362
00:19:40,950 --> 00:19:43,610
Quick, take off your clothes
and give them to me.

363
00:19:44,400 --> 00:19:45,200
The old rules.

364
00:19:45,310 --> 00:19:46,910
Do exactly as you did before.

365
00:19:47,480 --> 00:19:48,610
No matter who comes later,

366
00:19:48,610 --> 00:19:49,810
just pretend to be me.

367
00:19:54,170 --> 00:19:55,990
[Zhengtong Bookstore]

368
00:19:54,480 --> 00:19:55,960
I didn't expect Your Highness

369
00:19:55,960 --> 00:19:57,640
to have such insight and literary talent.

370
00:19:57,640 --> 00:19:58,500
I am impressed.

371
00:19:58,790 --> 00:19:59,920
You flatter me, sir.

372
00:20:00,350 --> 00:20:01,070
Thanks to

373
00:20:01,070 --> 00:20:03,130
the books you copied for me last time,

374
00:20:03,400 --> 00:20:04,590
I benefited a lot.

375
00:20:05,310 --> 00:20:07,480
But I still have a few doubts here.

376
00:20:07,790 --> 00:20:09,590
I hope you can explain them to me.

377
00:20:10,680 --> 00:20:11,610
Confucius said,

378
00:20:11,790 --> 00:20:15,000
"Zilu, do you understand
what true knowledge is?

379
00:20:15,880 --> 00:20:17,590
To know what you know, and admit

380
00:20:17,590 --> 00:20:19,070
what you do not know—

381
00:20:19,920 --> 00:20:21,120
that is true wisdom."

382
00:20:37,350 --> 00:20:39,880
Have you ever been to Yingzhou?

383
00:20:41,660 --> 00:20:42,350
No.

384
00:20:43,340 --> 00:20:45,050
Why the question?

385
00:20:46,790 --> 00:20:49,510
It's just that you look

386
00:20:49,960 --> 00:20:51,620
exactly like a friend of mine.

387
00:20:52,030 --> 00:20:53,310
He was from Yingzhou.

388
00:20:54,550 --> 00:20:56,240
Is it Mr. Pei?

389
00:20:56,430 --> 00:20:57,260
Yes.

390
00:20:58,000 --> 00:20:59,200
He has passed away.

391
00:21:02,440 --> 00:21:03,240
I see.

392
00:21:04,200 --> 00:21:06,720
The Pei family in Yingzhou
is a prominent family.

393
00:21:06,720 --> 00:21:09,680
Young Master Pei must also come
from a prestigious family

394
00:21:09,680 --> 00:21:10,790
and be a man of extraordinary talent.

395
00:21:10,790 --> 00:21:11,960
I am just a commoner,

396
00:21:12,950 --> 00:21:15,010
and dare not compare myself with him.

397
00:21:42,640 --> 00:21:44,960
Yuanji is meeting her lover here?

398
00:21:45,670 --> 00:21:46,800
Sorry to interrupt.

399
00:21:52,680 --> 00:21:53,210
Nanxing?

400
00:21:54,350 --> 00:21:56,240
Your Highness, My Lady is missing.

401
00:21:56,240 --> 00:21:56,920
She suspects

402
00:21:56,920 --> 00:21:58,920
that the Heir's Consort might be involved
in Cui Jun's disappearance.

403
00:21:58,920 --> 00:22:00,030
Today, when the Heir's Consort went out,

404
00:22:00,030 --> 00:22:01,270
she followed her.

405
00:22:02,040 --> 00:22:03,570
I knew it was related to her.

406
00:22:03,750 --> 00:22:05,150
Why did she get involved?

407
00:22:05,420 --> 00:22:07,200
Your Highness, you really knew it?

408
00:22:07,200 --> 00:22:08,460
I didn't know you knew.

409
00:22:08,590 --> 00:22:09,850
When Lady Xie asked me,

410
00:22:09,920 --> 00:22:12,830
I even said with absolute certainty
that you didn't know.

411
00:22:12,830 --> 00:22:13,440
At 5 p.m.,

412
00:22:13,440 --> 00:22:14,880
the Heir's Consort had already returned.

413
00:22:14,880 --> 00:22:16,500
But My Lady hasn't returned yet.

414
00:22:16,500 --> 00:22:17,350
Where are the Shadow Envoys?

415
00:22:17,350 --> 00:22:19,790
My Lady found a way to unlock the secret
of the Phoenix Heart Token.

416
00:22:19,790 --> 00:22:21,290
But she needs the Shadow Envoys
to leave the city to confirm it.

417
00:22:21,290 --> 00:22:22,630
The ones who should be here are absent.

418
00:22:22,630 --> 00:22:25,630
And the ones who shouldn't be here
are running around.

419
00:22:38,400 --> 00:22:40,400
If you want to see Xie Jiayu alive,

420
00:22:40,730 --> 00:22:43,460
bring all the Phoenix Heart Tokens
to Antai Gate.

421
00:22:57,440 --> 00:22:58,300
My little lady,

422
00:22:59,400 --> 00:23:00,600
you've been drugged.

423
00:23:01,640 --> 00:23:02,790
Don't waste your energy.

424
00:23:02,790 --> 00:23:04,640
Cui Jun, why did you kidnap me?

425
00:23:10,030 --> 00:23:11,200
I once had an eagle

426
00:23:11,270 --> 00:23:12,070
named Mingdi.

427
00:23:14,350 --> 00:23:16,950
I found it
when I was tending the herd as a child.

428
00:23:17,030 --> 00:23:18,640
It was shot by a hunter

429
00:23:19,310 --> 00:23:20,270
and was dying.

430
00:23:21,240 --> 00:23:22,310
I saved it.

431
00:23:22,590 --> 00:23:24,510
Since then, it has always been with me.

432
00:23:24,510 --> 00:23:25,750
But since I came to Southern Ye,

433
00:23:25,750 --> 00:23:26,810
it's been 20 years.

434
00:23:27,310 --> 00:23:28,750
I've never seen it again.

435
00:23:30,270 --> 00:23:31,590
It must be dead.

436
00:23:32,030 --> 00:23:33,200
Or it was caught by someone,

437
00:23:33,200 --> 00:23:34,260
cooked, and eaten.

438
00:23:34,790 --> 00:23:35,590
Or its feathers were

439
00:23:35,590 --> 00:23:36,590
plucked one by one

440
00:23:36,660 --> 00:23:37,490
to make a fan.

441
00:23:42,680 --> 00:23:43,480
Don't bother.

442
00:23:46,920 --> 00:23:47,720
Stop!

443
00:23:48,310 --> 00:23:49,510
Take one more step,

444
00:23:49,630 --> 00:23:51,230
and this little girl is dead.

445
00:23:51,270 --> 00:23:51,880
Jiayu!

446
00:23:51,960 --> 00:23:52,510
Cui Jun,

447
00:23:52,880 --> 00:23:53,640
let her go.

448
00:23:53,640 --> 00:23:55,040
Xie Jiayu is just a woman.

449
00:23:55,440 --> 00:23:56,550
Whatever happens

450
00:23:56,820 --> 00:23:58,070
has nothing to do with her.

451
00:23:58,070 --> 00:24:00,720
How could the woman cherished
by both His Highness and the Regent

452
00:24:00,720 --> 00:24:02,320
have nothing to do with this?

453
00:24:02,350 --> 00:24:03,790
Put your weapons down!

454
00:24:18,030 --> 00:24:19,830
You brought the Phoenix Heart Token,
right?

455
00:24:19,830 --> 00:24:20,790
Of course.

456
00:24:22,830 --> 00:24:23,550
Cui Jun,

457
00:24:23,760 --> 00:24:25,070
even if you get the tokens,

458
00:24:25,070 --> 00:24:26,510
you won't be able to escape.

459
00:24:26,510 --> 00:24:27,770
Who said I'm escaping?

460
00:24:29,240 --> 00:24:29,920
Xiao Wuyi,

461
00:24:30,310 --> 00:24:31,720
you and Xie Jiayu put on

462
00:24:31,720 --> 00:24:32,720
a good show.

463
00:24:33,000 --> 00:24:35,070
The token used to frame Li Lejun

464
00:24:35,350 --> 00:24:37,280
belongs to the Xiao family, right?

465
00:24:37,680 --> 00:24:39,080
And Her Highness's token

466
00:24:39,350 --> 00:24:40,920
is still in Li Mao's hands.

467
00:24:41,270 --> 00:24:41,930
It's yours.

468
00:24:46,550 --> 00:24:47,880
As long as you let her go,

469
00:24:48,160 --> 00:24:50,110
I will trade my life for hers.

470
00:24:51,750 --> 00:24:54,510
It seems Prince Qi really cares for you.

471
00:24:55,400 --> 00:24:56,860
He didn't hesitate at all.

472
00:24:57,440 --> 00:24:58,200
Xiao Wuyi,

473
00:24:59,030 --> 00:25:00,030
what about yours?

474
00:25:02,110 --> 00:25:03,970
I do have the Phoenix Heart Token.

475
00:25:05,270 --> 00:25:07,070
But what if I don't give it to you?

476
00:25:08,750 --> 00:25:09,480
Little girl.

477
00:25:10,650 --> 00:25:12,110
Prince Qi is a good choice.

478
00:25:13,110 --> 00:25:14,240
Xiao Wuyi is no good.

479
00:25:14,270 --> 00:25:15,310
In his eyes,

480
00:25:15,910 --> 00:25:17,570
you're not even worth a token.

481
00:25:17,750 --> 00:25:18,350
Wuyi.

482
00:25:19,240 --> 00:25:20,500
Yaoyao is in his hands.

483
00:25:20,590 --> 00:25:24,030
Whoever you choose to die today will die.

484
00:25:24,670 --> 00:25:25,590
I won't choose.

485
00:25:25,640 --> 00:25:26,400
Choose one.

486
00:25:26,920 --> 00:25:30,050
One is willing to give up the
Phoenix Heart Token for you.

487
00:25:30,920 --> 00:25:33,120
The other doesn't care about you at all.

488
00:25:35,510 --> 00:25:36,110
Xiao Wuyi.

489
00:25:36,420 --> 00:25:36,900
I...

490
00:25:37,270 --> 00:25:38,110
Let me go!

491
00:25:39,000 --> 00:25:39,720
Jiayu.

492
00:25:41,030 --> 00:25:41,880
Make a choice.

493
00:25:43,070 --> 00:25:44,270
No one will blame you.

494
00:25:59,400 --> 00:26:00,310
Ashina Qi.

495
00:26:03,240 --> 00:26:04,830
Why make things difficult for her?

496
00:26:04,830 --> 00:26:07,110
I will naturally give you
the Phoenix Heart Token.

497
00:26:07,110 --> 00:26:09,580
You used the Phoenix Heart Token
to drive a wedge

498
00:26:09,580 --> 00:26:11,770
between the court and its ministers.

499
00:26:13,680 --> 00:26:15,080
Since that's the case...

500
00:26:19,220 --> 00:26:20,400
Xiao Wuyi, stop!

501
00:26:20,430 --> 00:26:21,630
I will choose for you!

502
00:26:22,480 --> 00:26:23,310
I will take...

503
00:26:24,510 --> 00:26:25,510
Prince Qi's life.

504
00:26:25,680 --> 00:26:26,270
Good.

505
00:26:26,830 --> 00:26:27,830
If you kill him,

506
00:26:28,070 --> 00:26:29,670
I'll let this little girl go.

507
00:26:30,350 --> 00:26:30,950
Prince Qi,

508
00:26:31,400 --> 00:26:32,240
didn't you say

509
00:26:32,440 --> 00:26:34,840
you're willing
to trade your life for hers?

510
00:26:35,010 --> 00:26:36,280
I'll grant your wish.

511
00:26:36,310 --> 00:26:37,640
Xiao Wuyi, stop!

512
00:26:37,680 --> 00:26:40,310
Xiao Wuyi, I knew
I was right about you.

513
00:26:40,960 --> 00:26:44,020
You really have no respect
for the ruler or your father!

514
00:26:44,270 --> 00:26:45,000
Xiao Wuyi!

515
00:26:45,510 --> 00:26:46,910
He is the current Regent.

516
00:26:47,000 --> 00:26:48,240
This is the Antai Gate.

517
00:26:48,240 --> 00:26:49,530
Are you trying to rebel?

518
00:26:49,530 --> 00:26:50,450
Stop talking.

519
00:26:50,830 --> 00:26:52,440
If Xiao Wuyi really wants to rebel,

520
00:26:52,440 --> 00:26:54,070
are you going to fight him to the death?

521
00:26:54,070 --> 00:26:55,000
Xiao Wuyi,

522
00:26:55,640 --> 00:26:56,960
if you dare to shoot,

523
00:26:57,060 --> 00:26:58,770
it will be an act of regicide.

524
00:27:39,680 --> 00:27:40,310
Tell me,

525
00:27:40,550 --> 00:27:41,610
who kidnapped you?

526
00:27:52,440 --> 00:27:53,400
Mingdi.

527
00:27:56,200 --> 00:27:57,710
It has always been here.

528
00:28:02,030 --> 00:28:04,160
It's here to take me home.

529
00:28:08,000 --> 00:28:09,070
Mingdi.

530
00:28:09,960 --> 00:28:11,720
My Mingdi.

531
00:28:27,160 --> 00:28:28,000
Xiao Wuyi

532
00:28:28,270 --> 00:28:30,930
still didn't bring out
the Phoenix Heart Token.

533
00:28:32,480 --> 00:28:35,480
Li Mao is still not as calm
and steady as Xiao Wuyi.

534
00:28:36,110 --> 00:28:38,830
That arrow aimed at Prince Qi
was always meant to be fired.

535
00:28:38,830 --> 00:28:41,000
Now, everyone in the court

536
00:28:41,000 --> 00:28:43,260
saw Xiao Wuyi shoot an arrow at Prince Qi.

537
00:28:43,920 --> 00:28:45,350
Such disloyalty and treason...

538
00:28:45,350 --> 00:28:47,070
what a pleasant surprise.

539
00:28:47,480 --> 00:28:49,480
Your Majesty, by releasing Cui Jun,

540
00:28:49,830 --> 00:28:51,270
you have achieved two goals at once.

541
00:28:51,270 --> 00:28:52,070
It's truly brilliant.

542
00:28:52,070 --> 00:28:53,130
Really brilliant.

543
00:28:53,640 --> 00:28:54,720
Her Majesty

544
00:28:55,270 --> 00:28:57,310
doesn't want to keep dragging this out
with you

545
00:28:57,310 --> 00:28:59,440
and is willing to give you two ways out.

546
00:28:59,440 --> 00:29:00,480
One,

547
00:29:01,240 --> 00:29:02,510
die right now.

548
00:29:03,310 --> 00:29:04,400
The other,

549
00:29:05,000 --> 00:29:06,200
let you out.

550
00:29:06,200 --> 00:29:07,270
Out?

551
00:29:08,070 --> 00:29:09,930
As a secret agent of Northern Qin,

552
00:29:10,310 --> 00:29:11,510
you've done so much.

553
00:29:12,920 --> 00:29:15,510
You just want to see Ye in chaos, right?

554
00:29:16,200 --> 00:29:19,830
Now, Her Majesty is willing
to give you this chance.

555
00:29:25,750 --> 00:29:26,550
Your Majesty,

556
00:29:27,110 --> 00:29:30,200
are you still going to get rid
of Prince Qi?

557
00:29:31,030 --> 00:29:31,720
I think

558
00:29:32,420 --> 00:29:33,950
it's better to win him over.

559
00:29:35,510 --> 00:29:39,110
Look at Li Lejun. She used to pretend
to be so obedient and harmless.

560
00:29:39,110 --> 00:29:39,920
And now?

561
00:29:40,480 --> 00:29:42,350
Whether it's Li Mao or Li Lejun,

562
00:29:42,750 --> 00:29:45,480
they are nothing but wolves
in sheep's clothing.

563
00:29:45,550 --> 00:29:47,310
It's fine that they have yet
to fully spread their wings.

564
00:29:47,310 --> 00:29:48,590
But, if the day comes

565
00:29:48,750 --> 00:29:50,110
when Li Mao uses the Beifu Reform

566
00:29:50,110 --> 00:29:51,510
to establish his own authority,

567
00:29:51,510 --> 00:29:53,240
where would you and His Majesty

568
00:29:53,270 --> 00:29:54,720
stand?

569
00:29:58,880 --> 00:29:59,830
Young Lord Xiao,

570
00:29:58,960 --> 00:30:03,120
[Ziji Palace]

571
00:30:00,110 --> 00:30:01,960
Her Majesty is angry.

572
00:30:02,960 --> 00:30:06,220
Not only because
you pointed your arrow at Prince Qi today,

573
00:30:06,310 --> 00:30:08,000
breaking the rules of a subject,

574
00:30:08,000 --> 00:30:10,070
but also because you and Lady Xie

575
00:30:10,350 --> 00:30:11,750
committed the crime
of deceiving the throne.

576
00:30:11,750 --> 00:30:12,920
How is this deceiving the throne?

577
00:30:12,920 --> 00:30:13,750
Lady Xie,

578
00:30:14,400 --> 00:30:16,070
His Highness Prince Qi
has already handed over

579
00:30:16,070 --> 00:30:17,640
the third Phoenix Heart Token.

580
00:30:17,640 --> 00:30:18,510
His token

581
00:30:18,510 --> 00:30:20,840
is the one Li Lejun took
from Her Highness.

582
00:30:21,270 --> 00:30:24,350
Then where did the Phoenix Heart Token
that appeared

583
00:30:24,350 --> 00:30:26,150
at the palace banquet come from?

584
00:30:26,480 --> 00:30:29,540
You and Young Lord Xiao, in order
to catch the murderer,

585
00:30:29,560 --> 00:30:31,380
even dared to use Her Majesty
as part of your plan.

586
00:30:31,380 --> 00:30:33,520
Isn't this deceiving the throne?

587
00:30:34,550 --> 00:30:35,480
Xiao Wuyi,

588
00:30:36,830 --> 00:30:37,960
do you plead guilty?

589
00:30:39,510 --> 00:30:40,310
Your Majesty,

590
00:30:40,550 --> 00:30:41,830
the Phoenix Heart Token from that day

591
00:30:41,830 --> 00:30:43,790
was indeed granted
by Empress Wenxi to my father

592
00:30:43,790 --> 00:30:44,990
and passed down to me.

593
00:30:45,550 --> 00:30:46,810
To catch the murderer,

594
00:30:47,030 --> 00:30:48,160
I used Your Majesty.

595
00:30:48,510 --> 00:30:49,370
I plead guilty.

596
00:30:51,480 --> 00:30:53,230
But Xie Jiayu was only acting out
of concern for her mother.

597
00:30:53,230 --> 00:30:54,230
She meant no harm.

598
00:30:54,720 --> 00:30:58,050
And the injustice she presented
was not a false accusation.

599
00:30:58,680 --> 00:31:00,160
Please show mercy, Your Majesty.

600
00:31:00,160 --> 00:31:02,510
I am willing to take the punishment
for Lady Xie as well.

601
00:31:02,510 --> 00:31:04,070
Such devotion.

602
00:31:04,510 --> 00:31:06,040
Then I will grant your wish.

603
00:31:07,110 --> 00:31:08,240
You shall

604
00:31:08,480 --> 00:31:09,940
take her flogging as well.

605
00:31:10,400 --> 00:31:11,800
Thank you, Your Majesty.

606
00:31:17,770 --> 00:31:19,100
No, I plead guilty, too.

607
00:31:19,680 --> 00:31:20,740
Let's split it half and half.

608
00:31:20,740 --> 00:31:23,400
You shouldn't
take the beating all by yourself.

609
00:31:35,720 --> 00:31:36,310
Start it.

610
00:31:37,680 --> 00:31:38,940
Begin the punishment.

611
00:32:02,270 --> 00:32:02,960
Xiao Wuyi!

612
00:32:06,680 --> 00:32:07,640
Lady Xie,

613
00:32:07,920 --> 00:32:09,080
if you stop it,

614
00:32:09,110 --> 00:32:10,880
it will not only be deceiving the throne

615
00:32:10,880 --> 00:32:12,940
but also defying an imperial decree.

616
00:32:15,960 --> 00:32:16,560
Continue.

617
00:32:17,160 --> 00:32:18,440
Xiao Wuyi!

618
00:32:20,160 --> 00:32:20,830
No!

619
00:32:23,960 --> 00:32:25,400
No!

620
00:32:29,110 --> 00:32:31,110
Do you understand what it means
to be ruler and subject?

621
00:32:31,110 --> 00:32:32,350
You were born to be a ruler.

622
00:32:32,350 --> 00:32:34,680
If you refuse to become Crown Prince Wenxi

623
00:32:34,680 --> 00:32:36,590
and sit on that throne in Jiankang Palace,

624
00:32:36,590 --> 00:32:38,000
choosing instead
to remain a subject for life

625
00:32:38,000 --> 00:32:39,510
even with Beifu Army in your hands,

626
00:32:39,510 --> 00:32:41,160
you will still be feared and restrained
by others all your life.

627
00:32:41,160 --> 00:32:42,880
Your every move will be constrained.

628
00:32:42,880 --> 00:32:44,070
If I sit on that throne,

629
00:32:44,070 --> 00:32:45,870
will I be free from constraints?

630
00:32:47,070 --> 00:32:48,300
With the noble families
controlling the military,

631
00:32:48,300 --> 00:32:49,680
whoever sits in that position

632
00:32:49,680 --> 00:32:51,070
will inevitably be constrained.

633
00:32:51,070 --> 00:32:52,870
That's why I established Beifu,

634
00:32:53,240 --> 00:32:55,830
an army that doesn't belong
to the noble families.

635
00:32:55,830 --> 00:32:56,920
I want countless common-born talents

636
00:32:56,920 --> 00:32:58,880
to have the chance to make their mark
and find a place in this world.

637
00:32:58,880 --> 00:32:59,590
Even if the noble families

638
00:32:59,590 --> 00:33:01,320
can never truly be suppressed,

639
00:33:01,370 --> 00:33:02,830
I still want to bring fresh blood

640
00:33:02,830 --> 00:33:03,760
into Ye's court.

641
00:33:06,830 --> 00:33:08,690
There are many things I need to do,

642
00:33:10,790 --> 00:33:12,520
but I don't have much time left.

643
00:33:12,880 --> 00:33:13,810
What do you mean?

644
00:33:14,510 --> 00:33:16,480
I was injured at Jiuzhang Plain,

645
00:33:16,920 --> 00:33:18,720
and my lifespan is compromised.

646
00:33:21,590 --> 00:33:23,390
Heaven didn't give me more time.

647
00:33:28,270 --> 00:33:30,530
Heaven's will abandoned me 25 years ago.

648
00:33:31,240 --> 00:33:32,900
What I seek is not that throne.

649
00:33:34,540 --> 00:33:35,480
If I don't want the Beifu Army

650
00:33:35,480 --> 00:33:37,010
to disappear with my death,

651
00:33:37,720 --> 00:33:39,110
I must do more things,

652
00:33:39,750 --> 00:33:42,410
rather than merely sitting
above everyone else

653
00:33:42,750 --> 00:33:45,080
and negotiating with the noble families.

654
00:33:47,200 --> 00:33:48,310
You trust Prince Qi

655
00:33:49,350 --> 00:33:51,080
and are willing to support him?

656
00:33:51,880 --> 00:33:53,680
Perhaps as Xie Jiayu's husband,

657
00:33:54,510 --> 00:33:56,770
he is not satisfactory to Your Highness.

658
00:33:58,070 --> 00:33:59,530
But I know he has ambition.

659
00:34:02,070 --> 00:34:03,030
What if one day

660
00:34:04,400 --> 00:34:06,130
you find he doesn't deserve it?

661
00:34:27,440 --> 00:34:28,760
In your future actions,

662
00:34:28,760 --> 00:34:31,219
can you spare a little thought
for yourself?

663
00:34:31,480 --> 00:34:32,150
Today,

664
00:34:32,360 --> 00:34:33,070
you actually aimed your bow

665
00:34:33,070 --> 00:34:34,360
at Mao in public.

666
00:34:36,030 --> 00:34:37,489
Are you worried about Mao?

667
00:34:37,510 --> 00:34:38,880
I'm not joking with you.

668
00:34:39,710 --> 00:34:40,590
Neither am I.

669
00:34:54,030 --> 00:34:54,880
In the past,

670
00:34:55,590 --> 00:34:57,400
I heard many rumors about you.

671
00:34:58,110 --> 00:34:59,280
Because of them,

672
00:35:00,400 --> 00:35:03,230
I was very afraid of you
and doubted you

673
00:35:03,880 --> 00:35:05,740
when I first entered the mansion.

674
00:35:07,550 --> 00:35:09,070
If it weren't for the fact that

675
00:35:09,070 --> 00:35:11,190
we've been through so many things
together later,

676
00:35:11,190 --> 00:35:13,590
I wouldn't have gotten to know
the real you.

677
00:35:14,840 --> 00:35:15,900
And I wouldn't have

678
00:35:19,670 --> 00:35:21,230
fallen for you.

679
00:35:32,070 --> 00:35:33,000
What did you say?

680
00:35:38,880 --> 00:35:39,590
I mean,

681
00:35:49,000 --> 00:35:49,760
Xiao Wuyi,

682
00:35:53,190 --> 00:35:54,670
I'm in love with you.

683
00:36:05,030 --> 00:36:07,190
If we are merely traveling the same road,

684
00:36:07,190 --> 00:36:09,720
when our paths diverge, we must part ways.

685
00:36:11,880 --> 00:36:12,550
Xiao Wuyi,

686
00:36:14,710 --> 00:36:17,170
I don't just want
to walk the same path as you.

687
00:36:17,800 --> 00:36:18,840
I want to walk it

688
00:36:19,590 --> 00:36:20,920
to the very end with you.

689
00:36:28,070 --> 00:36:29,510
So from now on,

690
00:36:30,000 --> 00:36:32,660
could you please think
about yourself a little?

691
00:36:33,190 --> 00:36:34,850
If you have a good reputation,

692
00:36:35,000 --> 00:36:36,710
even if you make mistakes in the future,

693
00:36:36,710 --> 00:36:38,150
people will still believe you.

694
00:36:38,150 --> 00:36:40,610
Wouldn't it be easier
to achieve your goals?

695
00:36:44,230 --> 00:36:47,160
Look how good the Grand Tutor
is at deceiving people.

696
00:36:48,880 --> 00:36:50,480
Everyone says you are smart,

697
00:36:50,710 --> 00:36:52,570
but why do I think you are foolish?

698
00:36:54,760 --> 00:36:55,880
In the court,

699
00:36:56,760 --> 00:36:58,490
someone must play the villain,

700
00:36:58,880 --> 00:37:00,740
and someone must play the savior.

701
00:37:01,670 --> 00:37:04,470
I've already chosen someone
to play the good side.

702
00:37:05,050 --> 00:37:06,910
I don't mind playing the villain.

703
00:37:07,150 --> 00:37:09,610
Have you ever thought
about your own ending?

704
00:37:11,720 --> 00:37:13,450
Although I don't like reading,

705
00:37:13,770 --> 00:37:15,300
I've read many storybooks.

706
00:37:16,110 --> 00:37:17,920
Throughout history, subjects

707
00:37:18,800 --> 00:37:21,730
who love playing the villain like you
never end well.

708
00:37:26,480 --> 00:37:27,110
Yes.

709
00:37:29,480 --> 00:37:31,740
So I dare not expect to keep you
by my side.

710
00:37:35,230 --> 00:37:36,760
What if I insist?

711
00:37:39,630 --> 00:37:40,480
Can you

712
00:37:42,640 --> 00:37:44,300
take better care of yourself?

713
00:37:52,320 --> 00:37:54,520
You told me to treat this place
as my home

714
00:37:54,760 --> 00:37:56,760
and promised Mother
to keep me safe.

715
00:37:57,550 --> 00:37:59,350
But I know what you're thinking.

716
00:38:00,000 --> 00:38:02,660
You would simply arrange
a hundred or so guards,

717
00:38:03,590 --> 00:38:06,920
and if something happened
to you or the Xiao family in the future,

718
00:38:06,920 --> 00:38:09,010
they would escort me away. Am I right?

719
00:38:11,330 --> 00:38:13,330
I don't want to rely on you like this.

720
00:38:20,110 --> 00:38:21,310
Then what do you want?

721
00:38:27,350 --> 00:38:30,190
What if I don't want
to be the wife of the infamous Demon Xiao,

722
00:38:30,190 --> 00:38:31,550
but the wife of a hero?

723
00:38:37,390 --> 00:38:38,430
I want you

724
00:38:41,270 --> 00:38:42,400
to live a long life,

725
00:38:43,390 --> 00:38:44,470
to live in peace,

726
00:38:47,250 --> 00:38:49,110
to leave behind an honorable name,

727
00:38:49,110 --> 00:38:50,640
and to be remembered by all.

728
00:38:57,900 --> 00:39:00,100
You are making things difficult for me.

729
00:39:03,980 --> 00:39:04,780
That's right.

730
00:39:05,790 --> 00:39:07,020
I insist on doing so.

731
00:39:09,110 --> 00:39:10,310
Will you listen to me?

732
00:39:17,180 --> 00:39:21,570
♪ Let me dash toward where you are ♪

733
00:39:21,590 --> 00:39:25,020
♪ To seek out my own sanctuary ♪

734
00:39:25,050 --> 00:39:27,830
♪ Life hurries by, yet you alone ♪

735
00:39:27,860 --> 00:39:30,860
♪ Illuminate me
with your blazing radiance ♪

736
00:39:30,880 --> 00:39:34,930
♪ Let me burn with courage
as I forge ahead ♪

737
00:39:34,960 --> 00:39:38,440
♪ Your hand in my hand ♪

738
00:39:38,470 --> 00:39:41,390
♪ Our love knows no bounds
of time or space ♪

739
00:39:38,590 --> 00:39:39,150
I...

740
00:39:41,410 --> 00:39:46,940
♪ Two hearts together
until the end of time ♪

741
00:39:45,070 --> 00:39:45,840
I'll try.

742
00:39:53,760 --> 00:39:55,090
Then I promise you, too.

743
00:39:58,190 --> 00:40:02,050
♪ Let me dash toward where you are ♪

744
00:39:58,440 --> 00:39:59,770
I will always choose you

745
00:40:00,760 --> 00:40:01,710
and trust you.

746
00:40:02,250 --> 00:40:05,680
♪ To seek out my own sanctuary ♪

747
00:40:03,190 --> 00:40:03,990
In the future,

748
00:40:05,700 --> 00:40:08,490
♪ Life hurries by, yet you alone ♪

749
00:40:07,030 --> 00:40:08,670
treat this place as your own home.

750
00:40:08,510 --> 00:40:11,510
♪ Illuminate me
with your blazing radiance ♪

751
00:40:11,540 --> 00:40:15,590
♪ Let me burn with courage
as I forge ahead ♪

752
00:40:15,620 --> 00:40:19,100
♪ Your hand in my hand ♪

753
00:40:19,120 --> 00:40:22,050
♪ Our love knows no bounds
of time or space ♪

754
00:40:22,070 --> 00:40:27,600
♪ Two hearts together
until the end of time ♪

755
00:40:22,320 --> 00:40:23,030
Yaoyao.

756
00:40:25,310 --> 00:40:27,110
Since you've made your promise,

757
00:40:29,030 --> 00:40:31,760
no matter who tries
to take you away in the future,

758
00:40:32,600 --> 00:40:36,660
♪ Let me burn with courage
as I forge ahead ♪

759
00:40:33,760 --> 00:40:35,440
I will never let you go again.

760
00:40:36,680 --> 00:40:40,160
♪ Your hand in my hand ♪

761
00:40:40,190 --> 00:40:43,110
♪ Our love knows no bounds
of time or space ♪

762
00:40:43,130 --> 00:40:48,660
♪ Two hearts together
until the end of time ♪

